VLSM Message Properties

Section equivocator_vlsm_message_properties.

Lifting properties about sent messages to the equivocators

In this section we first prove some general properties about sent messages being preserved and reflected by the equivocator_vlsm, and then we show that the has_been_sent_capability and the computable_sent_messages can be lifted (each separately) from the original machine to the equivocator_vlsm. 
Context
  {message : Type}
  (X : VLSM message)
  (equivocator_vlsm := equivocator_vlsm X)
  (MachineDescriptor := MachineDescriptor X)
  .
If a projection of an equivocator_vlsm trace outputs a message, then the original trace must do so too. 
message:Type
X:VLSM message
equivocator_vlsm:=Common.equivocator_vlsm X:VLSM message
MachineDescriptor:=Common.MachineDescriptor X:Type
tr:list (vtransition_item equivocator_vlsm)
trX:list (vtransition_item X)
j, i:MachineDescriptor
HtrX:equivocator_vlsm_trace_project X tr j =
Some (trX, i)
m:message
Hjbs:Exists (field_selector output m) trX
Exists (field_selector output m) tr

message:Type
X:VLSM message
equivocator_vlsm:=Common.equivocator_vlsm X:VLSM message
MachineDescriptor:=Common.MachineDescriptor X:Type
a:vtransition_item equivocator_vlsm
tr:list (vtransition_item equivocator_vlsm)
j:MachineDescriptor
m:message
IHtr:forall trX : list (vtransition_item X),
Exists (field_selector output m) trX ->
forall i : MachineDescriptor,
equivocator_vlsm_trace_project X tr j =
Some (trX, i) ->
Exists (field_selector output m) tr
trX:list (vtransition_item X)
Hjbs:Exists (field_selector output m) trX
i:MachineDescriptor
HtrX:match
  equivocator_vlsm_trace_project X tr j
with
| Some (r, idescriptor) =>
    match
      equivocator_vlsm_transition_item_project
        X a idescriptor
    with
    | Some (Some item', odescriptor) =>
        Some (item' :: r, odescriptor)
    | Some (None, odescriptor) =>
        Some (r, odescriptor)
    | None => None
    end
| None => None
end = Some (trX, i)
Exists (field_selector output m) (a :: tr)

    
message:Type
X:VLSM message
equivocator_vlsm:=Common.equivocator_vlsm X:VLSM message
MachineDescriptor:=Common.MachineDescriptor X:Type
a:vtransition_item equivocator_vlsm
tr:list (vtransition_item equivocator_vlsm)
j:MachineDescriptor
m:message
trX':list (vtransition_item X)
i':Common.MachineDescriptor X
Htr:equivocator_vlsm_trace_project X tr j =
Some (trX', i')
IHtr:forall trX : list (vtransition_item X),
Exists (field_selector output m) trX ->
forall i : MachineDescriptor,
Some (trX', i') = Some (trX, i) ->
Exists (field_selector output m) tr
trX:list (vtransition_item X)
Hjbs:Exists (field_selector output m) trX
i:MachineDescriptor
HtrX:match
  equivocator_vlsm_transition_item_project X a
    i'
with
| Some (Some item', odescriptor) =>
    Some (item' :: trX', odescriptor)
| Some (None, odescriptor) =>
    Some (trX', odescriptor)
| None => None
end = Some (trX, i)
Exists (field_selector output m) (a :: tr)

message:Type
X:VLSM message
equivocator_vlsm:=Common.equivocator_vlsm X:VLSM message
MachineDescriptor:=Common.MachineDescriptor X:Type
a:vtransition_item equivocator_vlsm
tr:list (vtransition_item equivocator_vlsm)
j:MachineDescriptor
m:message
trX':list (vtransition_item X)
i':Common.MachineDescriptor X
Htr:equivocator_vlsm_trace_project X tr j =
Some (trX', i')
IHtr:Exists (field_selector output m) trX' ->
forall i : MachineDescriptor,
Some (trX', i') = Some (trX', i) ->
Exists (field_selector output m) tr
item':vtransition_item X
Hjbs:Exists (field_selector output m)
  (item' :: trX')
i:MachineDescriptor
Hitem':exists (i : nat) (is_equiv : bool),
  i' = Existing X i is_equiv /\
  proper_descriptor X i' (destination a) /\
  input a = input item' /\
  output a = output item'
Exists (field_selector output m) (a :: tr)

message:Type
X:VLSM message
equivocator_vlsm:=Common.equivocator_vlsm X:VLSM message
MachineDescriptor:=Common.MachineDescriptor X:Type
bs:vstate equivocator_vlsm
btr:list (vtransition_item equivocator_vlsm)
Hbtr:finite_protocol_trace_from
  (pre_loaded_with_all_messages_vlsm
     equivocator_vlsm) bs btr
bitem:vtransition_item equivocator_vlsm
Hitem:In bitem btr
sn:state
Hnew:snd (l bitem) = NewMachine X sn
input bitem = None /\
output bitem = None /\
(exists d : MachineDescriptor,
   equivocator_vlsm_transition_item_project X bitem d =
   Some (None, snd (l bitem)))


message:Type
X:VLSM message

  (pre_loaded_with_all_messages_vlsm
     equivocator_vlsm) bs btr
bitem:vtransition_item equivocator_vlsm
Hitem:In bitem btr
sn:state
Hnew:snd (l bitem) = NewMachine X sn
input bitem = None /\
output bitem = None /\
(exists d : MachineDescriptor,
   equivocator_vlsm_transition_item_project X bitem d =
   Some (None, snd (l bitem)))

  
message:Type
X:VLSM message
equivocator_vlsm:=Common.equivocator_vlsm X:VLSM message
MachineDescriptor:=Common.MachineDescriptor X:Type
bs:vstate equivocator_vlsm
btr:list (vtransition_item equivocator_vlsm)
Hbtr:finite_protocol_trace_from
  (pre_loaded_with_all_messages_vlsm
     equivocator_vlsm) bs btr
bitem:vtransition_item equivocator_vlsm
Hitem:exists
  l1
   l2 : list
          (vtransition_item equivocator_vlsm),
  btr = l1 ++ bitem :: l2
sn:state
Hnew:snd (l bitem) = NewMachine X sn
input bitem = None /\
output bitem = None /\
(exists d : MachineDescriptor,
   equivocator_vlsm_transition_item_project X bitem d =
   Some (None, snd (l bitem)))

  (pre_loaded_with_all_messages_vlsm
     equivocator_vlsm) s bsuffix

  (pre_loaded_with_all_messages_vlsm
     equivocator_vlsm) l 
  (lst, iom) (s, oom)

input := iom;
destination := s;
output := oom |} = bitem

  {|
  l := l;
  input := iom;
  destination := s;
  output := oom |} = None /\

  {|
  l := l;
  input := iom;
  destination := s;
  output := oom |} = None /\

     {|
     l := l;

     destination := s;
     output := oom |} d =
   Some
     (None,
     snd
       (Common.l
          {|
          l := l;
          input := iom;
          destination := s;
          output := oom |})))

message:Type
X:VLSM message
equivocator_vlsm:=Common.equivocator_vlsm X:VLSM message
MachineDescriptor:=Common.MachineDescriptor X:Type
bs:vstate equivocator_vlsm
bitem:vtransition_item equivocator_vlsm
bprefix, bsuffix:list (vtransition_item equivocator_vlsm)
Hbprefix:finite_protocol_trace_from
  (pre_loaded_with_all_messages_vlsm
     equivocator_vlsm) bs bprefix
lst:state
Heqlst:lst = finite_trace_last bs bprefix
Hbsuffix:finite_protocol_trace_from
  (pre_loaded_with_all_messages_vlsm
     equivocator_vlsm) lst
  (bitem :: bsuffix)
sn, s:state
iom, oom:option message
l:vlabel X
H2:finite_protocol_trace_from
  (pre_loaded_with_all_messages_vlsm
     equivocator_vlsm) s bsuffix
Hpitem:forall (fi : bool) (sn0 : state),
NewMachine X sn = NewMachine X sn0 ->
exists (i : nat) (_ : i < S (projT1 s)),
  equivocator_vlsm_transition_item_project X
    bitem (Existing X i fi) =
  Some (None, NewMachine X sn)
H:{|
l := (l, NewMachine X sn);
input := iom;
destination := s;
output := oom |} = bitem
Ht:transition (l, NewMachine X sn) (lst, iom) =
(s, oom)
Hv:valid (l, NewMachine X sn) (lst, iom)
iom = None /\
oom = None /\
(exists d : MachineDescriptor,
   equivocator_vlsm_transition_item_project X bitem d =
   Some (None, NewMachine X sn))

Qed.
For any transition_item in a protocol trace segment of an equivocator_vlsm there exists a projection of that trace containing the projection of the item. 
message:Type
X:VLSM message
equivocator_vlsm:=Common.equivocator_vlsm X:VLSM message
MachineDescriptor:=Common.MachineDescriptor X:Type
bs, bf:vstate equivocator_vlsm
btr:list (vtransition_item equivocator_vlsm)
Hbtr:finite_protocol_trace_from_to
  (pre_loaded_with_all_messages_vlsm
     equivocator_vlsm) bs bf btr
bitem:vtransition_item equivocator_vlsm
Hitem:In bitem btr
idl:nat
fdl:bool
Hlbitem:snd (l bitem) = Existing X idl fdl
exists item : vtransition_item X,
  (exists d : MachineDescriptor,
     equivocator_vlsm_transition_item_project X bitem
       d = Some (Some item, snd (l bitem))) /\
  (exists tr : list (vtransition_item X),
     In item tr /\
     (exists dfinal dfirst : MachineDescriptor,
        proper_descriptor X dfirst bs /\
        not_equivocating_descriptor X dfinal
          (finite_trace_last bs btr) /\
        equivocator_vlsm_trace_project X btr dfinal =
        Some (tr, dfirst)))


message:Type
X:VLSM message
equivocator_vlsm:=Common.equivocator_vlsm X:VLSM message

btr:list (vtransition_item equivocator_vlsm)
Hbtr:finite_protocol_trace_from_to
  (pre_loaded_with_all_messages_vlsm
     equivocator_vlsm) bs bf btr
bitem:vtransition_item equivocator_vlsm
Hitem:In bitem btr
idl:nat
fdl:bool
Hlbitem:snd (l bitem) = Existing X idl fdl
exists item : vtransition_item X,
  (exists d : MachineDescriptor,
     equivocator_vlsm_transition_item_project X bitem
       d = Some (Some item, snd (l bitem))) /\
  (exists tr : list (vtransition_item X),
     In item tr /\
     (exists dfinal dfirst : MachineDescriptor,
        proper_descriptor X dfirst bs /\

          (finite_trace_last bs btr) /\
        equivocator_vlsm_trace_project X btr dfinal =

message:Type
X:VLSM message
equivocator_vlsm:=Common.equivocator_vlsm X:VLSM message
MachineDescriptor:=Common.MachineDescriptor X:Type
bs, bf:vstate equivocator_vlsm
btr:list (vtransition_item equivocator_vlsm)

  (pre_loaded_with_all_messages_vlsm
     equivocator_vlsm) bs bf btr

idl:nat
fdl:bool
Hlbitem:snd (l bitem) = Existing X idl fdl
Hinv2:btr <> [] ->
finite_protocol_trace_from_to
  (pre_loaded_with_all_messages_vlsm
     (Common.equivocator_vlsm X)) bs bf btr ->
forall (j : nat) (fj : bool)
  (di : Common.MachineDescriptor X)
  (trX : list (vtransition_item X)),
equivocator_vlsm_trace_project X btr
  (Existing X j fj) = Some (trX, di) ->
exists Hj : j < S (projT1 bf),
  match di with
  | NewMachine _ sn =>
      finite_protocol_trace_init_to
        (pre_loaded_with_all_messages_vlsm X)
        sn (projT2 bf (of_nat_lt Hj)) trX
  | Existing _ i _ =>
      exists Hi : i < S (projT1 bs),
        let s := projT2 bs (of_nat_lt Hi) in
        let f := projT2 bf (of_nat_lt Hj) in
        finite_protocol_trace_from_to
          (pre_loaded_with_all_messages_vlsm X)
          s f trX /\
        (vinitial_state_prop
           (pre_loaded_with_all_messages_vlsm
              (Common.equivocator_vlsm X)) bs ->
         vinitial_state_prop
           (pre_loaded_with_all_messages_vlsm
              X) s)
  end
exists item : vtransition_item X,
  (exists d : MachineDescriptor,
     equivocator_vlsm_transition_item_project X bitem
       d = Some (Some item, snd (l bitem))) /\
  (exists tr : list (vtransition_item X),
     In item tr /\
     (exists dfinal dfirst : MachineDescriptor,
        proper_descriptor X dfirst bs /\
        not_equivocating_descriptor X dfinal
          (finite_trace_last bs btr) /\
        equivocator_vlsm_trace_project X btr dfinal =
        Some (tr, dfirst)))

  (pre_loaded_with_all_messages_vlsm

        not_equivocating_descriptor X dfinal
          (finite_trace_last bs
             (bprefix ++ bitem :: bsuffix)) /\
        equivocator_vlsm_trace_project X
          (bprefix ++ bitem :: bsuffix) dfinal =
        Some (tr, dfirst)))

equivocator_vlsm:=Common.equivocator_vlsm X:VLSM message
MachineDescriptor:=Common.MachineDescriptor X:Type
bs, bf:vstate equivocator_vlsm
bitem:vtransition_item equivocator_vlsm
bprefix, bsuffix:list (vtransition_item equivocator_vlsm)
lst:state
Heqlst:lst = finite_trace_last bs bprefix
Hbprefix:finite_protocol_trace_from_to
  (pre_loaded_with_all_messages_vlsm
     equivocator_vlsm) bs lst bprefix
Hbsuffix:finite_protocol_trace_from_to
  (pre_loaded_with_all_messages_vlsm
     equivocator_vlsm) lst bf
  (bitem :: bsuffix)
idl:nat
fdl:bool
Hlbitem:(let (_, y) :=
   let (l, _, _, _) := bitem in l in
 y) = Existing X idl fdl
Hinv2:forall (j : nat) (fj : bool)
  (di : Common.MachineDescriptor X)
  (trX : list (vtransition_item X)),
equivocator_vlsm_trace_project X
  (bprefix ++ bitem :: bsuffix)
  (Existing X j fj) = Some (trX, di) ->
exists Hj : j < S (projT1 bf),
  match di with
  | NewMachine _ sn =>
      finite_protocol_trace_init_to
        (pre_loaded_with_all_messages_vlsm X)
        sn (projT2 bf (of_nat_lt Hj)) trX
  | Existing _ i _ =>
      exists Hi : i < S (projT1 bs),
        finite_protocol_trace_from_to
          (pre_loaded_with_all_messages_vlsm X)
          (projT2 bs (of_nat_lt Hi))
          (projT2 bf (of_nat_lt Hj)) trX /\
        (vinitial_state_prop
           (pre_loaded_with_all_messages_vlsm
              (Common.equivocator_vlsm X)) bs ->
         vinitial_state_prop
           (pre_loaded_with_all_messages_vlsm
              X) (projT2 bs (of_nat_lt Hi)))
  end
s, f:state
iom, oom:option message
l:vlabel X
dl:Common.MachineDescriptor X
H3:finite_protocol_trace_from_to
  (pre_loaded_with_all_messages_vlsm
     equivocator_vlsm) s bf bsuffix
Hv:valid (l, dl) (lst, iom)
Ht:transition (l, dl) (lst, iom) = (s, oom)
H2:f = bf
H:{|
l := (l, dl);
input := iom;
destination := s;
output := oom |} = bitem
Hpitem:forall (fi : bool) (i : nat)
  (is_equiv : bool),
dl = Existing X i is_equiv ->
exists
  (i0 : nat) (_ : i0 < S (projT1 s)) 
(itemx : vtransition_item X),
  equivocator_vlsm_transition_item_project X
    bitem (Existing X i0 fi) =
  Some (Some itemx, dl)
exists item : vtransition_item X,
  (exists d : MachineDescriptor,
     equivocator_vlsm_transition_item_project X
       {|
       l := (l, dl);
       input := iom;
       destination := s;
       output := oom |} d = Some (Some item, dl)) /\
  (exists tr : list (vtransition_item X),
     In item tr /\
     (exists dfinal dfirst : MachineDescriptor,
        proper_descriptor X dfirst bs /\
        not_equivocating_descriptor X dfinal
          (finite_trace_last bs
             (bprefix ++
              {|
              l := (l, dl);
              input := iom;
              destination := s;
              output := oom |} :: bsuffix)) /\
        equivocator_vlsm_trace_project X
          (bprefix ++
           {|
           l := (l, dl);
           input := iom;
           destination := s;
           output := oom |} :: bsuffix) dfinal =
        Some (tr, dfirst)))

      finite_protocol_trace_init_to
        (pre_loaded_with_all_messages_vlsm X)
        sn (projT2 bf (of_nat_lt Hj)) trX
  | Existing _ i _ =>
      exists Hi : i < S (projT1 bs),
        finite_protocol_trace_from_to
          (pre_loaded_with_all_messages_vlsm X)
          (projT2 bs (of_nat_lt Hi))
          (projT2 bf (of_nat_lt Hj)) trX /\
        (vinitial_state_prop
           (pre_loaded_with_all_messages_vlsm
              (Common.equivocator_vlsm X)) bs ->
         vinitial_state_prop
           (pre_loaded_with_all_messages_vlsm
              X) (projT2 bs (of_nat_lt Hi)))

destination := projT2 s (of_nat_lt Hi);
output := oom |}
prefix:list (vtransition_item X)
dfirst:Common.MachineDescriptor X
Hprefix:equivocator_vlsm_trace_project X bprefix
  (Existing X idl fdl) =
Some (prefix, dfirst)
Htr:equivocator_vlsm_trace_project X
  (bprefix ++ [bitem] ++ bsuffix)
  (Existing X i false) =
Some (prefix ++ [itemx] ++ suffix, dfirst)
exists tr : list (vtransition_item X),
  In itemx tr /\
  (exists dfinal dfirst : MachineDescriptor,
     proper_descriptor X dfirst bs /\
     not_equivocating_descriptor X dfinal
       (finite_trace_last bs
          (bprefix ++ bitem :: bsuffix)) /\
     equivocator_vlsm_trace_project X
       (bprefix ++ bitem :: bsuffix) dfinal =
     Some (tr, dfirst))

l:vlabel X
H3:finite_protocol_trace_from
  (pre_loaded_with_all_messages_vlsm
     equivocator_vlsm) s bsuffix
Hv:valid (l, Existing X idl fdl)
  (finite_trace_last bs bprefix, iom)
Ht:transition (l, Existing X idl fdl)
  (finite_trace_last bs bprefix, iom) = 
(s, oom)
H2:f = bf
fsuffix:bool
dsuffix:Common.MachineDescriptor X
Heqdsuffix:dsuffix = Existing X i fsuffix
_Hitemx:equivocator_vlsm_transition_item_project X
  {|
  l := (l, Existing X idl fdl);
  input := iom;
  destination := s;
  output := oom |} dsuffix =
Some (Some itemx, Existing X idl fdl)
H:{|
l := (l, Existing X idl fdl);
input := iom;
destination := s;
output := oom |} = bitem
Hi:i < S (projT1 s)
dfinal:=Existing X i false:Common.MachineDescriptor X
Hsuffix:equivocator_vlsm_trace_project X bsuffix
  (Existing X i false) =
Some (suffix, dsuffix)
Hsuffix':equivocator_vlsm_trace_project X
  ([bitem] ++ bsuffix) 
  (Existing X i false) =
Some
  ([itemx] ++ suffix, Existing X idl fdl)
Hitem:equivocator_vlsm_trace_project X [bitem]
  dsuffix = Some ([itemx], Existing X idl fdl)
id:idl < S (projT1 (finite_trace_last bs bprefix))
Hvs':vvalid X (fst (l, Existing X idl fdl))
  (projT2 (finite_trace_last bs bprefix)
     (of_nat_lt id), iom)
Hts':vtransition X (fst (l, Existing X idl fdl))
  (projT2 (finite_trace_last bs bprefix)
     (of_nat_lt id), iom) =
(projT2 s (of_nat_lt Hi), oom)
Heqitemx:itemx =
{|
l := fst (l, Existing X idl fdl);
input := iom;
destination := projT2 s (of_nat_lt Hi);
output := oom |}
Hprefix:equivocator_vlsm_trace_project X bprefix
  (Existing X idl fdl) =
Some (prefix, dfirst)
Htr:equivocator_vlsm_trace_project X
  (bprefix ++ bitem :: bsuffix)
  (Existing X i false) =
Some (prefix ++ itemx :: suffix, dfirst)
exists dfinal dfirst : MachineDescriptor,
  proper_descriptor X dfirst bs /\
  not_equivocating_descriptor X dfinal
    (finite_trace_last bs
       (bprefix ++ bitem :: bsuffix)) /\
  equivocator_vlsm_trace_project X
    (bprefix ++ bitem :: bsuffix) dfinal =
  Some (prefix ++ itemx :: suffix, dfirst)

  
message:Type
X:VLSM message
equivocator_vlsm:=Common.equivocator_vlsm X:VLSM message
MachineDescriptor:=Common.MachineDescriptor X:Type
bs, bf:vstate equivocator_vlsm
bitem:vtransition_item equivocator_vlsm
bprefix, bsuffix:list (vtransition_item equivocator_vlsm)
Hbsuffix:finite_protocol_trace_from_to
  (pre_loaded_with_all_messages_vlsm
     equivocator_vlsm)
  (finite_trace_last bs bprefix) bf
  (bitem :: bsuffix)
Hbprefix:finite_protocol_trace_from_to
  (pre_loaded_with_all_messages_vlsm
     equivocator_vlsm) bs
  (finite_trace_last bs bprefix) bprefix
idl:nat
fdl:bool
i:nat
itemx:vtransition_item X
suffix, prefix:list (vtransition_item X)
dfirst:Common.MachineDescriptor X
Hdfinal:i < S (projT1 bf)
Hdinitial:match dfirst with
| NewMachine _ sn =>
    finite_protocol_trace_init_to
      (pre_loaded_with_all_messages_vlsm X)
      sn (projT2 bf (of_nat_lt Hdfinal))
      (prefix ++ itemx :: suffix)
| Existing _ i0 _ =>
    exists Hi : i0 < S (projT1 bs),
      finite_protocol_trace_from_to
        (pre_loaded_with_all_messages_vlsm
           X) (projT2 bs (of_nat_lt Hi))
        (projT2 bf (of_nat_lt Hdfinal))
        (prefix ++ itemx :: suffix) /\
      (vinitial_state_prop
         (pre_loaded_with_all_messages_vlsm
            (Common.equivocator_vlsm X))
         bs ->
       vinitial_state_prop
         (pre_loaded_with_all_messages_vlsm
            X) (projT2 bs (of_nat_lt Hi)))
end

Qed.
If an equivocator_vlsm's protocol trace segment outputs a message, then one of its projections must do so too. 
message:Type
X:VLSM message
equivocator_vlsm:=Common.equivocator_vlsm X:VLSM message
MachineDescriptor:=Common.MachineDescriptor X:Type
is:vstate equivocator_vlsm
tr:list (vtransition_item equivocator_vlsm)
Htr:finite_protocol_trace_from
  (pre_loaded_with_all_messages_vlsm
     equivocator_vlsm) is tr
m:message
Hbbs:Exists (field_selector output m) tr
exists
  (j i : MachineDescriptor) (_ : proper_descriptor X i
                                   is) (_ : not_equivocating_descriptor
                                              X j
                                              (finite_trace_last
                                                 is tr)) 
(trX : list (vtransition_item X)) (_ : equivocator_vlsm_trace_project
                                         X tr j =
                                       Some (trX, i)),
  Exists (field_selector output m) trX

message:Type
X:VLSM message
equivocator_vlsm:=Common.equivocator_vlsm X:VLSM message
MachineDescriptor:=Common.MachineDescriptor X:Type
is:vstate equivocator_vlsm
tr:list (vtransition_item equivocator_vlsm)
Htr:finite_protocol_trace_from_to
  (pre_loaded_with_all_messages_vlsm
     equivocator_vlsm) is
  (finite_trace_last is tr) tr
m:message
item:transition_item
Hin:In item tr
Houtput:field_selector output m item
i:nat
fi:bool
Hsndl:snd (l item) = Existing X i fi
Hitem:exists item0 : vtransition_item X,
  (exists d : MachineDescriptor,
     equivocator_vlsm_transition_item_project
       X item d =
     Some (Some item0, snd (l item))) /\
  (exists tr0 : list (vtransition_item X),
     In item0 tr0 /\
     (exists
        dfinal dfirst : MachineDescriptor,
        proper_descriptor X dfirst is /\
        not_equivocating_descriptor X dfinal
          (finite_trace_last is tr) /\
        equivocator_vlsm_trace_project X tr
          dfinal = Some (tr0, dfirst)))
exists
  (j i : MachineDescriptor) (_ : proper_descriptor X i
                                   is) (_ : not_equivocating_descriptor
                                              X j
                                              (finite_trace_last
                                                 is tr)) 
(trX : list (vtransition_item X)) (_ : equivocator_vlsm_trace_project
                                         X tr j =
                                       Some (trX, i)),
  Exists (field_selector output m) trX

  (finite_trace_last is tr)

                                              X j

                                                 is tr)) 
(trX : list (vtransition_item X)) (_ : equivocator_vlsm_trace_project

  Exists (field_selector output m) trX

message:Type
X:VLSM message
equivocator_vlsm:=Common.equivocator_vlsm X:VLSM message
MachineDescriptor:=Common.MachineDescriptor X:Type
is:vstate equivocator_vlsm
tr:list (vtransition_item equivocator_vlsm)
Htr:finite_protocol_trace_from_to
  (pre_loaded_with_all_messages_vlsm
     equivocator_vlsm) is
  (finite_trace_last is tr) tr
m:message
item:transition_item
Hin:In item tr
Houtput:field_selector output m item
i:nat
fi:bool
Hsndl:snd (l item) = Existing X i fi
itemx:vtransition_item X
d:MachineDescriptor
Hitemx:exists (i : nat) (is_equiv : bool),
  d = Existing X i is_equiv /\
  proper_descriptor X d (destination item) /\
  input item = input itemx /\
  output item = output itemx
trx:list (vtransition_item X)
Hinx:In itemx trx
ifinal, ifirst:MachineDescriptor
Hifirst:proper_descriptor X ifirst is
Hifinal:not_equivocating_descriptor X ifinal
  (finite_trace_last is tr)
Htrx:equivocator_vlsm_trace_project X tr ifinal =
Some (trx, ifirst)
field_selector output m itemx

     equivocator_vlsm) is
  (finite_trace_last is tr) tr

Section has_been_sent_lifting.

Lifting the has_been_sent_capability

Context
  {Hbs : has_been_sent_capability X}
  .
We define has_been_sent for the equivocator_vlsm as being sent by any of the internal machines. 
Definition equivocator_has_been_sent
  (s : vstate equivocator_vlsm)
  (m : message)
  : Prop
  :=
  let (n, bs) := s in
  exists i: Fin.t (S n), has_been_sent X (bs i) m.


message:Type
X:VLSM message
equivocator_vlsm:=Common.equivocator_vlsm X:VLSM message
MachineDescriptor:=Common.MachineDescriptor X:Type
Hbs:has_been_sent_capability X
RelDecision equivocator_has_been_sent


message:Type

MachineDescriptor:=Common.MachineDescriptor X:Type
Hbs:has_been_sent_capability X
RelDecision equivocator_has_been_sent

Hbs:has_been_sent_capability X
n:nat
bs:t (S n) -> vstate X
m:message
Decision
  (equivocator_has_been_sent
     (existT (fun n : nat => t (S n) -> vstate X) n bs)
     m)

The equivocator_vlsm has the selected_messages_consistency_prop for output messages, meaning that if a message is sent in a trace leading to state s, then it must be seen in all traces. 
message:Type

  (pre_loaded_with_all_messages_vlsm
     equivocator_vlsm) s
m:message
selected_messages_consistency_prop equivocator_vlsm
  (field_selector output) s m

  (Existing X j fj) = Some (trX, i)
Hsomex:Exists (field_selector output m) trX
Hntr:btr <> []
Hj:j < S (projT1 s)
Hi:match i with
| NewMachine _ sn =>
    finite_protocol_trace_init_to
      (pre_loaded_with_all_messages_vlsm X) sn
      (projT2 s (of_nat_lt Hj)) trX
| Existing _ i _ =>
    exists Hi : i < S (projT1 bis),
      finite_protocol_trace_from_to
        (pre_loaded_with_all_messages_vlsm X)
        (projT2 bis (of_nat_lt Hi))
        (projT2 s (of_nat_lt Hj)) trX /\
      (vinitial_state_prop
         (pre_loaded_with_all_messages_vlsm
            (Common.equivocator_vlsm X)) bis ->
       vinitial_state_prop
         (pre_loaded_with_all_messages_vlsm X)
         (projT2 bis (of_nat_lt Hi)))
end

  (pre_loaded_with_all_messages_vlsm X)

message:Type
X:VLSM message
equivocator_vlsm:=Common.equivocator_vlsm X:VLSM message
MachineDescriptor:=Common.MachineDescriptor X:Type
s:vstate equivocator_vlsm
m:message
j:nat
Hj:j < S (projT1 s)
Hall:selected_message_exists_in_all_preloaded_traces
  X (field_selector output)
  (projT2 s (of_nat_lt Hj)) m
bis:state
btr:list transition_item
Hbtr:finite_protocol_trace_init_to
  (pre_loaded_with_all_messages_vlsm
     equivocator_vlsm) bis s btr
trX:list (vtransition_item X)
di:Common.MachineDescriptor X
Hproject:equivocator_vlsm_trace_project X btr
  (Existing X j false) = 
Some (trX, di)
Hdi:match di with
| NewMachine _ sn =>
    finite_protocol_trace_init_to
      (pre_loaded_with_all_messages_vlsm X) sn
      (projT2 s (of_nat_lt Hj)) trX
| Existing _ i _ =>
    exists Hi : i < S (projT1 bis),
      let s0 := projT2 bis (of_nat_lt Hi) in
      let f := projT2 s (of_nat_lt Hj) in
      finite_protocol_trace_from_to
        (pre_loaded_with_all_messages_vlsm X) s0
        f trX /\
      (vinitial_state_prop
         (pre_loaded_with_all_messages_vlsm
            (Common.equivocator_vlsm X)) bis ->
       vinitial_state_prop
         (pre_loaded_with_all_messages_vlsm X)
         s0)
end
trace_has_message (field_selector output) m btr

    
message:Type
X:VLSM message
equivocator_vlsm:=Common.equivocator_vlsm X:VLSM message
MachineDescriptor:=Common.MachineDescriptor X:Type
s:vstate equivocator_vlsm
m:message
j:nat
Hj:j < S (projT1 s)
Hall:selected_message_exists_in_all_preloaded_traces
  X (field_selector output)
  (projT2 s (of_nat_lt Hj)) m
bis:state
btr:list transition_item
Hbtr:finite_protocol_trace_init_to
  (pre_loaded_with_all_messages_vlsm
     equivocator_vlsm) bis s btr
trX:list (vtransition_item X)
di:Common.MachineDescriptor X
Hproject:equivocator_vlsm_trace_project X btr
  (Existing X j false) = 
Some (trX, di)
Hdi:match di with
| NewMachine _ sn =>
    finite_protocol_trace_init_to
      (pre_loaded_with_all_messages_vlsm X) sn
      (projT2 s (of_nat_lt Hj)) trX
| Existing _ i _ =>
    exists Hi : i < S (projT1 bis),
      let s0 := projT2 bis (of_nat_lt Hi) in
      let f := projT2 s (of_nat_lt Hj) in
      finite_protocol_trace_from_to
        (pre_loaded_with_all_messages_vlsm X) s0
        f trX /\
      (vinitial_state_prop
         (pre_loaded_with_all_messages_vlsm
            (Common.equivocator_vlsm X)) bis ->
       vinitial_state_prop
         (pre_loaded_with_all_messages_vlsm X)
         s0)
end
Exists (field_selector output m) trX

     bs)

  (pre_loaded_with_all_messages_vlsm
     equivocator_vlsm) start
  (existT (fun n : nat => t (S n) -> vstate X) n
     bs) tr
Hpre:forall (j : nat)
  (Hj : j <
        S
          (projT1
             (existT
                (fun n : nat =>
                 t (S n) -> vstate X) n bs)))
  (jf : bool),
exists
  (tr0 : list (vtransition_item X)) 
(di : Common.MachineDescriptor X) 
(_ : equivocator_vlsm_trace_project X tr
       (Existing X j jf) = 
     Some (tr0, di)),
  match di with
  | NewMachine _ sn =>
      finite_protocol_trace_init_to
        (pre_loaded_with_all_messages_vlsm X)
        sn
        (projT2
           (existT
              (fun n : nat =>
               t (S n) -> vstate X) n bs)
           (of_nat_lt Hj)) tr0
  | Existing _ i _ =>
      exists Hi : i < S (projT1 start),
        let s := projT2 start (of_nat_lt Hi) in
        let f :=
          projT2
            (existT
               (fun n : nat =>
                t (S n) -> vstate X) n bs)
            (of_nat_lt Hj) in
        finite_protocol_trace_from_to
          (pre_loaded_with_all_messages_vlsm X)
          s f tr0 /\
        (vinitial_state_prop
           (pre_loaded_with_all_messages_vlsm
              (Common.equivocator_vlsm X))
           start ->
         vinitial_state_prop
           (pre_loaded_with_all_messages_vlsm X)
           s)
  end
trace_has_message (field_selector output) m tr

      (pre_loaded_with_all_messages_vlsm X) sn
      (projT2
         (existT
            (fun n : nat => t (S n) -> vstate X)
            ns bs) (of_nat_lt Hj)) trX
| Existing _ i _ =>
    exists Hi : i < S (projT1 is),
      finite_protocol_trace_from_to
        (pre_loaded_with_all_messages_vlsm X)
        (projT2 is (of_nat_lt Hi))
        (projT2
           (existT
              (fun n : nat => t (S n) -> vstate X)
              ns bs) (of_nat_lt Hj)) trX /\
      (vinitial_state_prop
         (pre_loaded_with_all_messages_vlsm
            (Common.equivocator_vlsm X)) is ->
       vinitial_state_prop
         (pre_loaded_with_all_messages_vlsm X)
         (projT2 is (of_nat_lt Hi)))
end
protocol_state_prop
  (pre_loaded_with_all_messages_vlsm X)
  (bs (of_nat_lt Hj))

Finally we define the has_been_sent_capability for the equivocator_vlsm. 
Definition equivocator_has_been_sent_capability
  : has_been_sent_capability equivocator_vlsm
  :=
  {|
    has_been_sent := equivocator_has_been_sent;
    proper_sent := equivocator_proper_sent;
    proper_not_sent := equivocator_proper_not_sent
  |}.

End has_been_sent_lifting.

Section computable_sent_messages_lifting.

Lifting the computable_sent_messages property

Context
  {Hsent_messages : computable_sent_messages X}
  (message_eq : EqDecision message)
  (Hbeen_sent_X := @computable_sent_messages_has_been_sent_capability message X Hsent_messages message_eq)
  .
We define the sent_messages_fn for the equivocator_vlsm as the union of all sent_messages_fn for its internal machines. 
Definition equivocator_sent_messages_fn
  (s : vstate equivocator_vlsm)
  : set message
  :=
  fold_right (set_union decide_eq) []
    (map (fun i => sent_messages_fn X (projT2 s i)) (fin_t_listing (S (projT1 s)))).
equivocator_sent_messages_fn captures all sent_messages for that state. 
message:Type
X:VLSM message
equivocator_vlsm:=Common.equivocator_vlsm X:VLSM message
MachineDescriptor:=Common.MachineDescriptor X:Type
Hsent_messages:computable_sent_messages X
message_eq:EqDecision message
Hbeen_sent_X:=computable_sent_messages_has_been_sent_capability
  X:has_been_sent_capability X
s:vstate equivocator_vlsm
Hs:protocol_state_prop
  (pre_loaded_with_all_messages_vlsm
     equivocator_vlsm) s
m:message
In m (equivocator_sent_messages_fn s) <->
(exists sm : sent_messages equivocator_vlsm s,
   ` sm = m)

Qed.
Finally, we define the computable_sent_messages instance for the equivocator_vlsm. Note that we can reuse the consistency property proved above since computable_sent_messages for X implies has_been_sent_capability. 
Definition equivocator_computable_sent_messages
  : computable_sent_messages equivocator_vlsm
  :=
  {|
    sent_messages_fn := equivocator_sent_messages_fn;
    sent_messages_full := equivocator_sent_messages_full;
    sent_messages_consistency := @equivocator_has_been_sent_consistency Hbeen_sent_X
  |}.

End computable_sent_messages_lifting.

End equivocator_vlsm_message_properties.
